name: Extensive Anaerobic Best 1min
description:
Your ability to produce high power efforts above threshold is a significant factor in racing. This session focuses on Extensive Anaerobic efforts of 1min. Because we are looking for maximal efforts in this area, full recovery is provided between each interval. 



While the session might look simple on paper, don't be fooled. This is a High-Intensity session with maximal effort. To help you judge your effort for this duration, you will be guided through the opening intervals before being provided with the opportunity to produce your best efforts in the finale.
